nodes.text: Between 3 BBY and 2 BBY, Sabine Wren and Garazeb Orrelios went on a mission to Thune City to recover cargo containers full of weapons and ship parts on behalf of the rebellion. The two were ambushed by the gangster Tomith Garbis and his goons, who attempted to claim the containers for the Garbis family. Although the rebels managed to get the upper hand and fly away with the cargo, they attracted the wrath of Lord Donith Garbis, who swore to avenge his family's honor.
